title: Adam Beasley on Dolphins offensive potential in 2018 (Football 05/29)
description:
Adam Beasley of the Miami Herald joins Will Brinson to break down the Dolphins offseason, including his prediction that the Dolphins will score 25 points a game, what Adam Gase likes about this particular roster and why they are a lock for the over of 5.5 games in 2018.
